      "content": "calling people doesnt change the fact that i have nothing left. it's not just money, it's like my whole future just evaporated. i'm just sitting here staring at the wall thinking how much easier it would be if i just didn't have to deal with the weight of this anymore. i'm already at the bottom, i might as well just stay here.",
